      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7'>Top 15 GDP Growth Countries</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' lmargin='225'>This bar chart showcases the top 10 countries with the highest GDP growth in 2022. Guyana leads the list with an extraordinary 180.4% growth, driven largely by its booming oil sector. Other notable countries include Ireland, Ethiopia, and Tajikistan, reflecting strong economic rebounds and sectoral growth across diverse regions </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
