    <worksheet name='3'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#4e79a7' fontname='Tableau Bold'>Global Average GDP Growth Trend (2014–2023) </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#0e0e0e' fontname='Tableau Medium' lmargin='225'>This line chart illustrates the global average GDP growth trend from 2014 to 2023. The data highlights a consistent pattern of modest economic growth, interrupted sharply in 2020 due to the COVID-19 pandemic. A strong recovery followed in 2021, though recent years suggest a return to more moderate growth levels as global markets adjust to post-pandemic realities.</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Medium' lmargin='225'>Æ </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
