            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#0e0e0e' fontname='.AppleSystemUIFont' lmargin='225'>This heat map visualizes year-wise GDP growth for G7 countries from 2008 to 2023. Each block represents a country’s performance in a given year, colored by the intensity of growth or decline. Red blocks denote recessionary periods (e.g., 2009, 2020), while green indicates growth recoveries.</run>
